FBIS3-15021 "drsov041_u_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-041 Document Type:Daily Report 2 Mar 1994 Latvia Fire at Paldiski Russian Military Base LD0103230694 Riga Radio Riga Network in Latvian 2100 GMT 1 Mar 94 LD0103230694 Riga Radio Riga Network Language: Latvian Article Type:BFN [Text] An event that is possibly linked to the Skrunda incident: On Monday evening at the closed Russian military unit in the Estonian town of Paldiski a fire broke out. At the Russian military unit the barracks were burned. The fire was brought under control after about 90 minutes. The Paldiski police were not allowed into the scene of the fire. Russian Army officers expressed the view that this was deliberate arson, motivated by the fact that part of the military site has been pulled down. Possibly the fire broke out as the result of soldiers' negligence.
